description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: I Think There is Something Dead in There Edition with Beer City Bruiser!!

We are back to full strength!  All the King's Horses and all the King's Men put Timmy back together again, and we are back on the right track!  Cruiser and Bruiser have jumped on their computin' machines and gathered some rather intriguing stories about the world and people falling apart, and much more this week just for you!

This week,  NASA caused a collision in Space that not even LiMu Emu, Doug, and Liberty Mutual will cover! California will turn you into compost, really! If a fairy laughs at you in a forest in Ireland, will anyone hear it, And, a woman dies in a department store restroom, and isn't discovered for FOUR DAYS!

Check out our new site, https://www.darknessradioshow.com/ to find all of our old archives, leave us a voice message for parashare, read our blogs, and much more!

Find out where Beer City Bruiser is holding his breath and needlepointing near you: https://twitter.com/bcbwinchester
